{"article_id":"m154qoO4z0jgUd6A","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"FILE -","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"In this Aug. 29 , 2019 file photo , Iranian Foreign Minister Mohammad Javad Zarif attends a forum","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"titled `` Common Security in the Islamic World ''","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"in Kuala Lumpur , Malaysia .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"In an interview","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"published by CNN Thursday , Sept. 19 , 2019 ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Zarif warned","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that any U.S. or Saudi military strike on Iran will result in `` all-out war . '","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"' It comes","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"after U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo called an attack on Saudi oil installations an `` act of war . ''","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"( AP Photo/Vincent Thian , File )","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"FILE -","depth":3},{"id":12,"text":"In this Aug. 29 , 2019 file photo , Iranian Foreign Minister Mohammad Javad Zarif attends a forum","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"titled `` Common Security in the Islamic World ''","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"in Kuala Lumpur , Malaysia .","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"In an interview","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"published by CNN Thursday , Sept. 19 , 2019 ,","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Zarif warned","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that any U.S. or Saudi military strike on Iran will result in `` all-out war . '","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"' It comes","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"after U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo called an attack on Saudi oil installations an `` act of war . ''","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"( AP Photo/Vincent Thian , File )","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"DUBAI , United Arab Emirates","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"( AP ) -","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"Any attack on Iran by the U.S. or Saudi Arabia will spark an \" all-out war , \"","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"Tehran ' s top diplomat warned Thursday ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"raising the stakes","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"as Washington and Riyadh weigh a response to a drone-and-missile strike on the kingdom ' s oil industry","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"that shook global energy markets .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"The comments by Foreign Minister Mohammad Javad Zarif represented the starkest warning yet by Iran in a long summer of mysterious attacks and incidents","depth":6},{"id":30,"text":"following the collapse of Iran ' s 2015 nuclear deal with world powers ,","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"more than a year after President Donald Trump unilaterally withdrew the U.S. from the accord .","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"They appeared to be aimed directly at U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo ,","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"who while on a trip to the region earlier referred to Saturday ' s attack in Saudi Arabia as an \" act of war . \"","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"Along with the sharp language , however , there also were signals from both sides","depth":6},{"id":35,"text":"of wanting to avoid a confrontation .","depth":6},{"id":36,"text":"On Thursday evening , a spokesman at Iran ' s mission to the United Nations said","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"Zarif and President Hassan Rouhani had received U.S. visas","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"to attend next week ' s annual U.N. General Assembly meeting in New York .","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"In his comments , Zarif sought to expose current strains between the Americans and the Saudis under Trump ,","depth":6},{"id":40,"text":"who long has criticized U.S. wars in the Middle East .","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"Trump ' s close relationship with Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman has been challenged by opponents","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"following the killing of Washington Post columnist Jamal Khashoggi last year in the Saudi Consulate in Istanbul and the kingdom ' s long , bloody war in Yemen .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"That country ' s Houthi rebels claimed the oil field attack Saturday in Saudi Arabia ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"although the U.S. alleges","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Iran carried it out .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"it is important for the Saudi government to understand what they ' re what they ' re trying to achieve .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Do they want to fight Iran until the last American soldier ?","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Is that their aim ? \"","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Zarif asked in a CNN interview .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"\" They can be assured","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"that this won ' t be the case ...","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"because Iran will defend itself . \"","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"Asked by the broadcaster","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"what would be the consequence of a U.S. or Saudi strike ,","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"Zarif bluntly said :","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"\" An all-out war . \"","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"\" I ' m making a very serious statement","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"that we don ' t want war .","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"We don ' t want to engage in a military confrontation , \"","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"\" We believe","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"that a military confrontation","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"based on deception","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"is awful . \"","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"Zarif ,","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"who was to travel to New York on Friday ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"added :","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"\" We ' ll have a lot of casualties ,","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"but we won ' t blink to defend our territory . \"","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Pompeo ,","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"who was in the United Arab Emirates ,","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"dismissed Zarif ' s remarks ,","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"saying :","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"\" I was here","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"( doing ) active diplomacy","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"while the foreign minister of Iran is threatening all-out war","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"to fight to the last American . \"","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"Pompeo said","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"he hoped","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Iran would choose a path toward peace ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"but he remained doubtful .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"He described \" an enormous consensus in the region \"","depth":8},{"id":84,"text":"that Iran carried out the attack .","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"\" There are still those today","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"who think ,","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"' Boy , if we just give Iran just a little bit more money","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"they ' ll become a peaceful nation , ' \"","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"\" We can see","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"that that does not work . \"","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Pompeo met Abu Dhabi ' s powerful crown prince , Sheikh Mohammed bin Zayed Al Nahyan .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"The UAE is a close ally of Saudi Arabia","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"and joined the kingdom in its war with the Houthi rebels in Yemen .","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"The 4-year-old war has killed tens of thousands of people","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"and destroyed much of the country ,","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"with millions more driven from their homes","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"and thrown into near starvation .","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"On Wednesday , Pompeo met with the Saudi crown prince in Jiddah about the attack on the kingdom ' s crucial oil processing facility and oil field ,","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"which cut its oil production in half .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"While Pompeo struck a hard line ,","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"Trump has been noncommittal on whether he would order U.S. military retaliation .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"He said separately Wednesday","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"that he is moving to increase financial sanctions on Tehran over the attack ,","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"without elaborating .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"Iran already is subject to a crushing American sanctions program","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"targeting its crucial oil industry .","depth":7},{"id":108,"text":"The UAE said","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"it had joined a U.S.-led coalition","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"to protect waterways across the Middle East","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"after the attack in Saudi Arabia .","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"The state-run WAM news agency quoted Salem al-Zaabi of the Emirati Foreign Ministry","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"as saying","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"the UAE joined the coalition","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"to \" ensure global energy security and the continued flow of energy supplies to the global economy . \"","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"Saudi Arabia joined the coalition on Wednesday .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"Australia , Bahrain and the United Kingdom also are taking part .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"The U.S. formed the coalition after attacks on oil tankers","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"that Washington blamed on Tehran ,","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"as well as Iran ' s seizure of tankers in the region .","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"Iran denies being behind the tanker explosions ,","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"although the attacks came","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"after Tehran threatened to stop oil exports from the Persian Gulf .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"Iraq said","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"it would not join the coalition .","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"The government in Baghdad ,","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"which is allied with both Iran and the U.S. ,","depth":9},{"id":128,"text":"has tried to keep a neutral stance amid the tensions .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"At a news conference Wednesday , the Saudis displayed broken and burned drones and pieces of a cruise missile","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"that military spokesman Col. Turki Al-Malki identified as Iranian weapons","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"collected after the attack .","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"He also played surveillance video","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"he said","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"showed a drone","depth":13},{"id":136,"text":"coming in from the north .","depth":13},{"id":137,"text":"Yemen is to the south of Saudi Arabia .","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"Eighteen drones and seven cruise missiles were launched in the assault ,","depth":14},{"id":139,"text":"Al-Malki said ,","depth":14},{"id":140,"text":"with three missiles failing to hit their targets .","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"He said","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"the cruise missiles had a range of 700 kilometers","depth":15},{"id":143,"text":"( 435 miles ) ,","depth":15},{"id":144,"text":"meaning they could not have been fired from inside Yemen .","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"That opinion was shared by weapons experts","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"who spoke to The .","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"French Foreign Minister Jean-Yves Le Drian similarly was skeptical of the Houthi claim of responsibility .","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"\" This is not very credible ,","depth":11},{"id":149,"text":"relatively speaking , \"","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"he told CNews television .","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"\" But we sent our experts","depth":9},{"id":152,"text":"to have our own vision of things . \"","depth":9},{"id":153,"text":"Separately , a U.N. panel of experts on Yemen arrived in Saudi Arabia","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"to investigate the attack ,","depth":9},{"id":155,"text":"U.N. spokesman Farhan Haq said .","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"writers David Rising in Berlin , Angela Charlton in Paris , Qassim Abdul-Zahra in Baghdad and Edith M. Lederer at the United Nations contributed .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":313,"left":178,"right":312,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":167